import { View, Image, ScrollView, TextInput ,StyleSheet,KeyboardAvoidingView, TouchableOpacity, Text} from 'react-native'

import logo from "../assets/images/logo.png";
import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native-safe-area-context';

Victor Hugo ou Marcel Proust n’ont pas vraiment respecté ce principe. Chez Proust, les phrases comptent en moyenne 43 mots contre une vingtaine en moyenne chez les écrivains de langue française.</Text>

                        </View> 
                    </View>
                    <View style={styles.align}>

                            />

                        <View>

}
    const styles = StyleSheet.create({
        container:{
            flex:1,
            justifyContent:'center',
            alignItems:'center',
            backgroundColor:'#F1F1F1',
        },
        align:{

            backgroundColor: '#D26767',

            fontSize: 20,
            borderColor: 'black',
            borderWidth: 2,
            borderRadius: 30,
            padding: 20,
            justifyContent:'center',
            alignItems:'center',
            marginTop: '2%',
            marginBottom: '2%',
            marginLeft: '16%',
            marginRight: '16%',

            borderRadius: 30,

            marginTop: '2%',
            marginBottom: '2%',
            marginLeft: '9.5%',
            marginRight: '9.5%',
        },
        back:{

        },
        decallage:{

        },
        imagelogo:{

            height: 100,
            resizeMode: "contain",
            marginLeft: '5%',
            padding: 10
        },
        imagelogoleft:{
            width: 100,
            height: 100,

        },
        txttittle:{
            fontWeight: 'bold',
            fontSize: 20,
            padding: 5,
            textAlign: 'center',
            marginLeft: '10%',
        },
        tittle:{
            fontWeight: 'bold',
            fontSize: 28,
            padding: 5,
            textAlign: 'center',
        },
        txtbox:{
            padding: 5,
            textAlign: 'center',
            marginLeft: '10%',
        },
    })


export default Meal_plan;
